author: Jack Horgan-Jones, Marie O'Halloran
title: Coronavirus: Relaxation of restrictions in Ireland is not a certainty, say officials
description: Chief medical officer says despite public frustration good work may easily be undone
content:
Public health officials have said there is no certainty restrictions will be relaxed next month, despite a range of positive data indicating significant suppression in growth of the Covid-19 virus.
